    <p>The Ryerson Career &amp; Co-op Centre offers a faculty-based model of operation to help your organization target the best and brightest that Ryerson University has to offer. We offer a wide range of events and programs to help you achieve your hiring goals and raise your brand profile.</p> 
<p>As every employer has unique needs, we encourage you to contact our office to discuss how we can individualize any of the opportunities listed below for your company or co-create brand new ideas with you.</p> 
