                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h2 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1584384191541-experiential-learning-at-ryerson" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#80cea60f-9944-478e-bca7-f6946dd152ca" href="#accordion-content-1584384191541-experiential-learning-at-ryerson" aria-controls="accordion-content-1584384191541-experiential-learning-at-ryerson" aria-expanded="false">
                            Experiential Learning at Ryerson
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1584384191541-experiential-learning-at-ryerson" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1584384191541-experiential-learning-at-ryerson">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1584384191541 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="ad838633-1e74-494e-bae1-f4ad4ec0b7e7" >

    <p>This is for any organization – not-for-profits, small &amp; medium enterprises, large corporations, and public sector organizations – who want to host experiential learning (EL) opportunities for students at Ryerson University.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>EL provides students with hands-on learning experiences that contribute to their personal and career development, and these opportunities come in a diverse and broad array of formats and structures like:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>internships</li> 
 <li>co-op and work placements</li> 
 <li>practicums</li> 
 <li>hackathons</li> 
 <li>project-based learning</li> 
 <li>community-driven research.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>Your organization can benefit when you partner with Ryerson University on EL projects and placements. Our students can provide you with fresh perspectives on challenges, new and creative ideas, a more diverse mindset, up-to-date knowledge and skills, and a talent pipeline for the future.</p> 
<p>For more information and guidance on how you can host Ryerson students for an EL experience with your organization, please fill out the form below. A member of our team will respond within two business days.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>We look forward to working with you.</p>
    





