    <p>If you want to interview Ryerson students and new grads, we can help*. For employers that have posted jobs via Ryerson’s online jobs portal, <a href="/content/ryerson/career-coop/employers/post-a-job.html">Magnet</a>, interviews can be arranged at no additional cost.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> 
